    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-07-23T21:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-07-23T21:00:00-05:00" n="996"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d996">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">890F.6363/56a: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister Resident in Saudi Arabia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moose</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-07-23T22:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 23, 1943—10 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>36. Please cable in confidential code, up-to-the minute report on present
                    activities of California-Arabian Company<note n="32" xml:id="d996fn32">The
                        California Arabian Standard Oil Company (Casoc).</note> in Saudi Arabia,
                    giving in detail, account of present drilling and exploration activities,
                    production, actual and potential, transportation arrangements <pb facs="0945"
                        n="933" xml:id="pg_933"/> and disposition of present production,
                    distribution activities within Saudi Arabia. Also please give account of any new
                    development in relationship to Saudi Arabian Government. It is realized that you
                    have kept Department well-informed on these matters but this request is to
                    assure that our information is complete and up to the minute. Please hold this
                    inquiry in utmost secrecy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
